## Roadmap

**Phase 1 — Certification (Current)**
Exam engine, all 14 TRL roles, all 3 WSC roles, document ingestion, PDF/DOCX support.

**Phase 2 — Full PWA**
Supabase backend, persistent member profiles, server-side certification tokens, 24-hour lockout enforcement, Discord OAuth, commissioner dashboard.

**Phase 3 — Incident Management**
Incident ticket filing, stewards workflow, PP tracking, BSAC referral pipeline.

**Phase 4 — Financial Engine**
Salary cap, DDV tracking, contract management, transfer market.

**Phase 5 — Federation Expansion**
Multi-league onboarding, cross-league certification recognition, PitBoss as infrastructure for any sim racing league worldwide — aligned with FIA Appendix E (Esports International Sporting Code, effective January 2026).

